extends ../_layouts/docs

block title
  title Getting Started | BitPay

append vars
  -var pageSelected = 'Docs'

  -var subpageSelected = 'Getting Started'

block information
  h2.header__bottom-border-left Getting Started
  p.lead BitPay’s <a href="/integrations">40+ bitcoin integrations</a> make accepting bitcoin payments fast and reliable. To get started, <a href="#">sign up for a BitPay account</a>.

  h3 Accepting a Bitcoin Payment
  p With bitcoin, there's no sensitive customer information to collect and store, and there are no cards to charge. Customers simply send bitcoin from their computer or mobile device directly to a bitcoin payment address.

  p Once received, BitPay converts the bitcoin to your preferred currency and adds the full amount of the payment – without fees – to your next BitPay account <a href="/docs/settlement">settlement</a>. Funds are then deposited to your bank account or bitcoin address.

  p You can accept bitcoin in a variety of ways. Choose a method below to get started.

  h4 Online Payments
  p Bitcoin makes the online payment experience simple and convenient for customers on any device – customers can pay with just two taps, no sensitive personal information needed.

  .padding-left
    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") E-Commerce Platform Integrations
    p Accepting bitcoin with our partner platforms can be as easy as flipping a switch. Find your integration in our <a href="/integrations">full list of integrations</a> for details.

    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") Shopping Cart Plug-Ins
    p If you're using one of the leading open source shopping cart software solutions, we probably have an integration for it. View our plug-in options on our Integrations page.

    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") Website Payment Buttons
    p Generate payment buttons for your website directly through your merchant dashboard. No code-wrangling required – just copy and paste into your page.


  h4 In-Store Payments
  p Merchants can use BitPay's retail payment tools alongside traditional point of sale systems to create a faster, hassle-free checkout experience for customers and staff.

  .padding-left
    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") Point-of-Sale Integrations
    p Merchants using our partner point of sale providers can activate bitcoin payments with just a few clicks.

    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") Bitcoin Checkout App
    p Bitcoin Checkout can be used to accept bitcoin payments on any iOS or Android smartphone or tablet.

  h4 Donations
  p Nonprofits can get a running start with bitcoin contributions with our donation buttons and hosted donation pages.

  .padding-left
    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") Donation Buttons
    p BitPay's <a href=https://bitpay.com/dashboard/merchant/create-donate> donation buttons </a> make it simple to accept contributions on your organization's website.

    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") Hosted Donation Pages
    p BitPay can also create and host a <a href=https://bitpay.com/dashboard/merchant/edit-donation-page?params=donation> donation page </a> for your organization.

  h4 Billing
  p Our billing tools allow merchants to receive payment for services and goods with rapid bitcoin invoicing.

  .padding-left
    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") Email Billing
    p Our dashboard billing tool allows for Send bitcoin invoices to your clients via email on a one-time or recurring basis.

    h5
      a.arrow-blue(href="#") Billing Service Integrations
    p Want to add bitcoin invoicing to your current billing platform or plug-in? We've built integrations for some of the leaders in billing and accounting services.


  h4 Mobile App Payments
  p <a href=https://bitpay.com/mobile> BitPay's mobile SDKs </a> can be used to build in-app payment functionality on all major platforms.
